### Get own notification inbox
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Mark a single notification as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notifId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin sends custom notification to specific users
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/custom
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userIds": ["{{userId}}"],
  "title": "Important update",
  "body": "Please review the newly published module."
}

###

### Admin sends custom notification to all guides
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/custom
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "role": "GUIDE",
  "title": "System maintenance",
  "body": "The platform will be unavailable on Sunday from 2am to 4am."
}
